title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-04-2014 FRI
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-04-2014 FRI...PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 4/4/14Friday, April 04, 2014 



Glenn talks about homosexuality and libertarianism,
    
       sharing his perspective on the firing of Mozilla CEO Brendan Eich

             and homosexuality itself in relation to God.

 Matt Bevin joins the program to discuss his Senate race
                                       against Mitch McConnell 


        and Glenn talks about Pat's new editorial on TheBlaze.com.


                 That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
